</S>
<S ID="99807">
SURVEY OF ASSOCIATIONS AND GROUPS OF OLDER ADULTS
</S>
<S ID="99961">
A major portion of the data was collected through direct contact with organizations of older adults and professionals working with this age group.
</S>
<S ID="100126">
