</S>
<S ID="101823">
Some examples are:
</S>
<S ID="101873">
the Canadian Association for Adult Education;
</S>
<S ID="101934">
the Canadian Association for Independent Living Centres;
</S>
<S ID="102029">
the Confédération des organismes provinciaux pour les personnes     handicappées (Quebec).
